	Ugly dance    
	 Berlin (Reuters): A group of four German high school students took first prize in the final of the Ugly Dance World Cup held in Hamburg. They convinced with epic ugliness, horrible appearance and their signature move  the Shy Dance, according to the competitions official website. But the competitions organisers said the ugly dance was not necessarily bad. Its so easy to dance nicely, but ugly dancing is an art. We like to call it ugly aesthetics, they said.    
	Natalie ire    
	 London (PTI): Actress Natalie Portmans role as a lesbian ballerina in Black Swan has generated plenty of Oscar buzz, but has soured her relations with her father. The actress shot some explicit sex scenes for Swan, souring her relations with her father, Avner Hershlag. Portman, 29, had turned down roles, including Lolita, but was determined to take on the role of troubled ballerina Nina.
                                                                                                                                                      
